{"tid":1242126,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"歐美大熱天然夢幻藍香蕉 蕉界Häagen-Dazs口感creamy味道似雪糕","createTime":"2019-06-19T02:56:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-20T11:15:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f45d0c02960e97e889d2330bffdf2d8bc79380fc","tid":1242126,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:56:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2375000/2378513/1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2375000%2F2378513%2F1_1024.jpg&h=0d034d45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n鍾意食香蕉的朋友要留意！平時只係會見到熟透的黃色香蕉及未熟的綠色香蕉，又或者有些人會見過紅色香蕉，但藍色香蕉你又見過未？最近歐美地區流行一種夢幻藍色香蕉，味道口感都似足雪糕，被譽為蕉界H&auml;agen-Dazs！<br />\n<br />\n夏天食蜜瓜、桃？原來已經out！最近網絡上面就瘋傳一款藍色香蕉，在歐美極受歡迎。呢隻名為Blue Java Banana的香蕉其實來自東南亞地區，有「雪糕香蕉」(Ice Cream Banana)之稱，原來因為食過的人都形容其味道似雪糕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2375000/2378513/Ice_Cream_Banana_Tree_450_1024x1024_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2375000%2F2378513%2FIce_Cream_Banana_Tree_450_1024x1024_600.jpg&h=6b3aeeef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n藍香蕉屬天然非基因改造的水果，未熟前有著夢幻的藍色，熟透後會變黃，果肉與普通香蕉一樣呈奶白色，不過口感就特別creamy，而且香味極濃，味道及口感都似雲呢嗱雪糕。<br />\n<br />\n不過呢款藍色香蕉香港就暫時未有，想食的朋友就可能要到外國旅行時留意下喇！"},{"pid":"54c326c62239a33a46255e3be7143695eb9ab113","tid":1242126,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-19T02:56:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://food.ulifestyle.com.hk/restaurant/news/detail/2378513/%E8%97%8D%E8%89%B2%E9%A6%99%E8%95%89-%E6%AD%90%E7%BE%8E%E5%A4%A7%E7%86%B1%E5%A4%A9%E7%84%B6%E5%A4%A2%E5%B9%BB%E8%97%8D%E9%A6%99%E8%95%89-%E8%95%89%E7%95%8CH%C3%A4agen-Dazs%E5%8F%A3%E6%84%9Fcreamy%E5%91%B3%E9%81%93%E4%BC%BC%E9%9B%AA%E7%B3%95/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ff